Project 1 Back Channel Application

1. Authors:
Aldo Valenti <avalent>
Chun He <che>
Jeremy  Aube <jjaube>

2. Test platforms
Capybara, Cucumber

3. Starting URL
http://127.0.0.1:3000

4. Command to start application
Start command: rails server
Development db:  rake db:migrate
Initial data loading (including default admin user): rake db:seed

5. Admin Info
Default admin user login: admin@glq.com/ruby4all
To create new admin user, use the "Manage User" Link, you can promote an existing user to an admin.

6. Other notes
Extra credit: Capybara is used for integration testing
Additional gem included: devise, capybara, cucumber, timecop



